00:26:25,892 --> 00:26:27,513
A turtle is a hell of a way to communicate.

536
00:26:27,613 --> 00:26:29,574
What would otherwise be the world's biggest tool tip

537
00:26:29,654 --> 00:26:30,654
to take you through all of that?

538
00:26:31,014 --> 00:26:32,715
So they don't need eyes, but they do need to be turtles.

